name: Lifestyle of a new age low-key investor poster
description:
50% of proceeds will be donated to thewereachfoundation.org for Haiti's earthquake victims.

"Lifestyle of a new age low key Investor."  The members of this cast are comprised of gold, crypto and real estate investors. Our cast was strategically assembled to showcase some of Miami's local businesses and professionals. Also local business owners make cameo appearances and product placements. The Blue Lagoon Redland Farm in Homestead, Florida, location was used in the film storyline, as an off-grid private meet up, where new age low key investors network.  

Executive Producer J. Classic-Maestro
Creative Director Maicol Diaz

Music produced by J. Classic-Maestro
featuring Guitarist- Corey Harvin 
Music Arrangement by Karim and Misled Rilla
